positive.review:
this game is an awesome rpg/fps/rougelike. the vast varieties and hero combos are nearly endless, not to mention the cool maps, enemies and bosses. however for someone who's used to fps style games, i would suggest the devs to add an admire toggle (that allows you to view your gear's details ect) and also add a little bit more customization to heros, like hats or accessories to flex your progress. 

for those struggling with crown prince v. lu wu (first boss) id recommend focusing on using fire buffs,(pyrodominance) fire weapons exclusively, timed dashing, use chain ability and aim for lu wu's head (weakspot) 


if you like cool guns, bossfights, chinese mythology and furries, then this game's for you!
